description: Case Logic is obsessed with organization! No matter who you are, what toys, tools or technology you have, where you are, or where you are going, Case Logic is your partner in managing the things that matter to you. We are the "stuff wranglers" that make life easier.  With this focus in mind, Caselogic introduces the ULB-116 16-Inch Laptop Backpack. Front pocket is uniquely designed to expand  when filled to reveal a complementary lining color through strategically placed slits in exterior fabric. One-of-a-kind aesthetic, Custom zipper pullers and signature lining fabric. Separate padded laptop compartment fit laptops up to 16-Inch. Front pocket expands to easily fit power cord and includes key fob for easy access to keys. Large main compartment with elevated mesh electronics pockets that fit gadgets of all sizes, such as iPod, digital camera, and e-book reader. Innovative strap management system keeps webbing straps contained and out of the way. Sleek, unique shape makes bag truly exceptional. 25 Year limited Warranty!
title: Case Logic ULB-116 16-Inch Laptop Backpack (Gray)
